	   <tr><td colspan=2>I believe having higher charisma increases the effectiveness of your alteration spells. This is why it is important for shamen, and to a greater degree, Enchanters. Their primary school is almost always alteration. All buffs and debuffs fall under that category. It also helps lower prices when you buy things, but that's not terribly important especially at higher levels. That being said, I put no points into Charisma as my Barb Shm and I haven't had any major problems yet. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
