	   <tr><td colspan=2>I really think we are one of the best classes. I have a 47 shaman on Karana and really enjoy much with him. In a group I can heal if 'm the only healer, buff and debuff I always do that of course, nuke when there is an enchanter and mana permits, dot if we're kiting (low mana or no tanks), or tank if I'm with pure casters (specially erudites who don't really like to be meleed). And soloing is easy too with pet, I can tank with him, using my Damage shield potions, regen, alacrity and fully buffed, or solo without pet using torgor's insects to pull and root and dot. And you can be sure to find easily a group at high level, your buffs and debuffs are really wanted.<br>&nbsp;<br>Aekhold Hiigaran<br>Oracle Barbare<br>Officier d'Odysse<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12603" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12603</a></td></tr>
